 Requirements:

Maximum age 40 years old;
Diploma or Bachelor’s Degree in Hospitality or equivalent from reputable university, with GPA min. 3,00;
At least 2 years of working experience in the related field as Hotel Manager (hotel industry);
Excellent marketing and business development skills;
Should be highly motivated and self driven  with strong analytical and conceptual thinking;
Mastering various skills such as managerial, problem solving, leadership, hospitality and interpersonal;
Good organizational and multitasking abilities;
Solid knowledge of Ms. Office, particularly Excel and Word;
Able to work in Bandung.

 Job Description:

Review and verify invoices/ employee expenses prior to payment : completeness of supporting, managers approval, cost code, identify withholding tax, correctness of VAT Slip, etc;
Prepare AP journal voucher upload and input payment to internet banking;
Maintain files and documentation thoroughly and accurately, in accordance with company policy and accepted accounting practices;
Prepare billing as per instruction received, input billing to system and ensure it is delivered to customer;
Monitoring incoming transfer from customer and perform cash application (identify bank charge & withholding tax deduction);
Prepare monthly taxes computation and returns ( e-SPT). Ensure submission within the deadline;
Monthly bank reconciliation & assist with month-end closing;
Assist with preparation of audit sampling package for external & internal audits;
Assist in maintaining accounting controls by following group policies & procedures and comply with local statutory requirements;
Support other team members as necessary

 
Requirements

Minimum Bachelor Degree from Accountancy major (GPA min 3.0)
Having at least 2 years relevant experience
Excellent organizing abilities
Good with numbers and figures and an analytical acumen
Great attention to detail & deadline-oriented
Good problem solving skills, basic accounting principles knowledge and multi-tasking skills
Professional attitude, reliable, team work
Required language(s): English, Bahasa Indonesia


Candidate must possess at least Bachelor's Degree in any field.
