Assistant responsibility of the General Manager's Office

Responsible for the drafting all of the company's work plan, work summary, administrative comprehensive annual report and resolutions, organization and preparation of relevant company-wide rules and regulations;
Responsible for the general manager's office meeting arrangements and the reporting of materials of various departments, the specific implementation of the work inspection briefing;
Responsible for the company's internal and external contracts, agreements of the organization audit, retention;
Responsible for the management of the company seal;
Assist the CEO to check the completion of the indicators of various departments;
Assist on project investment inspection, demonstration work;
Coordinate all the relevant matters of subordinate companies;
Responsible for superior and internal review of relevant documents and written information;
Responsible for assisting in the handling of emergencies and other administrative work assigned to the leadership.


